1. Official version infomation of lt18i:
    基带版本 : 8x55A-AAABQOAZM-203028D-56
    版本号   : 4.0.2.A.0.42

2. recoveryARC.img, an image to enter recovery mode
    fastboot boot recoveryARC.img

3. RootXperia_zhw325.zip, a rom package to root lt18i
    put it in SD card, and apply it to lt18i under recovery mode
